quote: The view that man was ever to be drawn by some vision of the unattainable shining ahead, doomed ever to aspire, but not to achieve, my life and my values could not bring me to that.
quote_letters: THE VIEW THAT MAN WAS EVER TO BE DRAWN BY SOME VISION OF THE UNATTAINABLE SHINING AHEAD DOOMED EVER TO ASPIRE BUT NOT TO ACHIEVE MY LIFE AND MY VALUES COULD NOT BRING ME TO THAT
